      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a definitive benchmark in JDM performance. This example features the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged 3.0L inline-six, functioning perfectly with its original sequential forced induction system. Power is managed via the highly sought-after Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec Torsen limited-slip differential. The undercarriage and suspension components are immaculate, retaining the factory double-wishbone configuration and structural rigidity. All body panels carry matching VIN tags, confirming an accident-free history and original factory tolerances. Inside, the cockpit is flawless with no UV degradation on the dash or wear on the seat bolsters. This is a rare, mechanically synchronized survivor suited for the most discerning enthusiast.",
